{"tid":2412260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2男傳染期頻拜年聚會累逾70人隔離 油塘警宿2中產樓共11廈強檢","createTime":"2021-02-18T02:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T07:09:36.000Z","uid":239336,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ac33777e515fc7c10b0713a6fe5b438bd88a30c8","tid":2412260,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"本港昨日（17日）新增16宗武漢肺炎確診，12宗是本地感染，10宗沒源頭。初步確診約10宗，3宗沒源頭。無源頭確診的屯門72歲翁，發病逾月至年初四才召救護車送院，其間幾乎日日去3間酒樓飲茶。另外2名無源頭確診男在傳染期間四出拜年或聚會，包括到元朗葡萄園別墅，連累逾70名親友入隔離營檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n多11棟大廈要強制檢測，包括爆疫的葵涌消防局，累計3名職員和1名緊密接觸者中招。<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">油塘警察宿舍高翔苑高鳳閣</span></span>、中產屋苑藍田匯景花園1座和紅磡維港‧星岸2座都要強檢。約2個月前強檢兼突擊封樓查驗的沙田乙明邨明恩樓，再要強檢。由於病毒潛伏期較長，10日前突擊封區檢測的鰂魚涌惠利大廈，須第二次強檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/TVR733NVF5EUNJAUXIOE2ANSI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FTVR733NVF5EUNJAUXIOE2ANSI4%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=cf997bbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FTVR733NVF5EUNJAUXIOE2ANSI4%2F&h=b2da2205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/TVR733NVF5EUNJAUXIOE2ANSI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n狗宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZPXzeBzXG8c/Xd6ij0H0gDI/AAAAAAAAK6Q/WRPuvIlE1xIYxkThHSMh8G51EkrIvCZfwCLcBGAsYHQ/w598-h370-n/1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZPXzeBzXG8c%2FXd6ij0H0gDI%2FAAAAAAAAK6Q%2FWRPuvIlE1xIYxkThHSMh8G51EkrIvCZfwCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fw598-h370-n%2F1.gif&h=0ec1df81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84e828748b3d22c545fc04ae46f50cd675f9c947","tid":2412260,"uid":367485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gi